		<title>3 Time-Saving Facebook Automated Rules to Try (+1 to Avoid!)</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/07/27/facebook-automated-rules</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Brett McHale]]></dc:creator>
